query:
SELECT id, customer_name,
       JSON_EXTRACT(calculations, '$.batteryBrand') as batteryBrand,
       JSON_EXTRACT(calculations, '$.batterySizeKwh') as batterySizeKwh,
       slide_count
FROM proposals
WHERE status = 'generated'
ORDER BY id DESC
LIMIT 28
